  "detailed_description": "<h1>New Mech Combat Simulator!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/c8aaf89b9c24d5b6f8cd9e19bb64d08a.avif?t=1772360513\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Robot Fury is a mech combat simulator where you can feel like a true robot warrior. Fight enemies with a powerful flamethrower, soar into battle with your jetpack, and finish off foes with precise machine gun headshots. Customize your mech and engage in exhilarating, epic battles!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/52c46fc10b654ee64a1aa6d10d275bdc.webp?t=1772360513\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/6b7ce86429df7ff55dfa459f948e7414.poster.avif?t=1772360513\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/6b7ce86429df7ff55dfa459f948e7414.webm?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/6b7ce86429df7ff55dfa459f948e7414.mp4?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Robot Fury</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Robot Fury is an exhilarating mech combat simulator that puts you in the cockpit of powerful, customizable robots. Experience the thrill of mechanized warfare as you engage in fierce battles using an array of weaponry, including flamethrowers, machine guns, and rocket launchers. Soar into combat with your jetpack and execute precise attacks to dominate your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/7955a1aa6d7c92b978fe71bde260ce78.webp?t=1772360513\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/422693eae6753cf8e4371ca8e640f3ca.poster.avif?t=1772360513\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/422693eae6753cf8e4371ca8e640f3ca.webm?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/422693eae6753cf8e4371ca8e640f3ca.mp4?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers a variety of missions and challenges, allowing you to test your combat skills and tactical decisions. Customize your mech to suit your playstyle, upgrade its weapons, and adapt its abilities to tackle different threats. With intense combat scenarios and dynamic environments, Robot Fury delivers a gripping and immersive experience where every battle is a chance to prove your prowess as a top mech pilot!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Robot Fury is a mech combat simulator where you can feel like a true robot warrior. Fight enemies with a powerful flamethrower, soar into battle with your jetpack, and finish off foes with precise machine gun headshots. Customize your mech and engage in exhilarating, epic battles!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/52c46fc10b654ee64a1aa6d10d275bdc.webp?t=1772360513\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/6b7ce86429df7ff55dfa459f948e7414.poster.avif?t=1772360513\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/6b7ce86429df7ff55dfa459f948e7414.webm?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/6b7ce86429df7ff55dfa459f948e7414.mp4?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Robot Fury</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Robot Fury is an exhilarating mech combat simulator that puts you in the cockpit of powerful, customizable robots. Experience the thrill of mechanized warfare as you engage in fierce battles using an array of weaponry, including flamethrowers, machine guns, and rocket launchers. Soar into combat with your jetpack and execute precise attacks to dominate your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/7955a1aa6d7c92b978fe71bde260ce78.webp?t=1772360513\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/422693eae6753cf8e4371ca8e640f3ca.poster.avif?t=1772360513\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/422693eae6753cf8e4371ca8e640f3ca.webm?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/422693eae6753cf8e4371ca8e640f3ca.mp4?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers a variety of missions and challenges, allowing you to test your combat skills and tactical decisions. Customize your mech to suit your playstyle, upgrade its weapons, and adapt its abilities to tackle different threats. With intense combat scenarios and dynamic environments, Robot Fury delivers a gripping and immersive experience where every battle is a chance to prove your prowess as a top mech pilot!</p>",
